'''Dafydd ap Maredudd ap Tudur''' was a Welsh poet in the later 15th century. 

Tudur's works include religious poems, and [[Eulogy|eulogies]] of Dafydd ab Owain (abbot of [[Strata Marcella]]), Dafydd Deuddwr, Hywel Colunwy, and Watcyn ap Tomas ap Rhoser. <ref>{{cite web|title=Dafydd ap Maredudd ap Tudur|url=http://yba.llgc.org.uk/en/s-DAFY-APM-1460.html|website=Dictionary of Welsh Biography|publisher=National Library of Wales|accessdate=8 November 2016}}</ref>

